'''Form AA-23-7022''' was a document distributed and processed by the [[Algarian Bureau of Planetary Information and Tourism]]. Public information about the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Algarian]] and the [[Algarian system/Legends|Algarian system]] were restricted without submission of this form along with a 150 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credit]] processing fee.

